  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crab Champions is a fast paced roguelike shooter. Travel solo or with friends across exotic islands defeating hordes of enemies, collecting loot and becoming as powerful as possible creating game breaking builds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/f75e0040c856e25aa83b804443b05fd5.poster.avif?t=1754771711\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/f75e0040c856e25aa83b804443b05fd5.webm?t=1754771711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/f75e0040c856e25aa83b804443b05fd5.mp4?t=1754771711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Run based: the fun of a looter shooter packed into intense 20-40 minute runs with the option to loop endlessly to survive as long as you can!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth and responsive movement and combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully crafted visuals with a focus on quality while maintaining high performance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An original soundtrack made specifically for the game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenges to unlock cosmetic skins and put your skills to the test in Nightmare difficulty with modifiers to spice things up even further</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or assemble a multiplayer squad: the game is balanced separately for different party sizes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every choice matters: each run presents you with different loot combinations, enemy types and tough decisions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo developed by the creator of Crab Rave 🦀</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No lootboxes, microtransactions or ANY additional purchases required- all content is available to unlock in game by playing<br>  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHAOTIC FUN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/be7b89ef923a322214a71e2139279a6f.poster.avif?t=1754771711\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/be7b89ef923a322214a71e2139279a6f.webm?t=1754771711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/be7b89ef923a322214a71e2139279a6f.mp4?t=1754771711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PARKOUR ISLANDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/67821d6fbb5f1cd141c990251ab2f1d6.poster.avif?t=1754771711\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/67821d6fbb5f1cd141c990251ab2f1d6.webm?t=1754771711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/67821d6fbb5f1cd141c990251ab2f1d6.mp4?t=1754771711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEEP BUILD CRAFTING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/f9cc0338287752685714fd852f8c06c6.poster.avif?t=1754771711\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/f9cc0338287752685714fd852f8c06c6.webm?t=1754771711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/f9cc0338287752685714fd852f8c06c6.mp4?t=1754771711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TONS OF LOOT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/3ecdadfee0e18bd81d22c60877d52bfd.poster.avif?t=1754771711\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/3ecdadfee0e18bd81d22c60877d52bfd.webm?t=1754771711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/774801/extras/3ecdadfee0e18bd81d22c60877d52bfd.mp4?t=1754771711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>WARNING: This game allows you to create over the top and visually intense builds that may create flashing lights that could be potentially unsuitable for those that have an epileptic condition.</p>",
